190
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,559
Dulu itu salahku.

191
00:10:28,359 --> 00:10:29,960
Kita lupakan masa lalu,

192
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:31,400
ulangi dari awal.

193
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,320
Aku pasti akan baik padamu, oke?

194
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,559
