195
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:41,280
Tidak terlambat.
Sama sekali tidak terlambat.

196
00:10:42,919 --> 00:10:43,919
Kita pergi ke luar negeri.

197
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,280
Bali, Chiang Mai, Dubai.

198
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:46,799
