tidak ada yang mengenal kita.

199
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,000
Kita mulai dari awal.

200
00:11:27,359 --> 00:11:28,359
Fanlu.

201
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,919
Apa yang kau lakukan?

202
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,280
Makan perlahan-lahan.

203
00:11:36,119 --> 00:11:36,919
Fanlu!

204
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:38,159
Fanlu!

205
00:11:43,359 --> 00:11:44,200
Tunggu.

206
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,119
