756
00:38:35,919 --> 00:38:37,280
Fanlu terkena penyakit depresi.

757
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,879
Sejak kapan?

758
00:38:39,719 --> 00:38:41,639
Kenapa kau tak bilang padaku dari awal?

759
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:45,199
Sebenarnya Fanlu sudah beberapa saat
menderita penyakit ini.

760
00:38:45,439 --> 00:38:48,080
Aku tak bilang padamu
karena takut kau khawatir.

761
00:38:49,959 --> 00:38:52,040
